iperf: iperf (a tool for measurement of bandwidth on IP networks)
iperf:
iperf: iperf is a tool for active measurement of the maximum achievable
iperf: bandwidth on IP networks.  It supports tuning of various parameters
iperf: related to timing, protocols, and buffers.  For each test it reports
iperf: the measured throughput / bitrate, loss, and other parameters.
